<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="328" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1358,2142,2726]" pageId="11" pageNumber="328">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[153,504,2497,2530]" pageId="11" pageNumber="328">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. Extent of occurrence of the Dwarf Gymnure is less than 20,000 km?, it is known from fewer than ten locations, and there is continuing decline in the extent and quality ofits habitat in the Sumatran Mountains.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
